data.description: Everyone loves a brick ranch with a basement! Immaculate home that is light and bright. Large foyer greets you upon entering and opens to the formal livingand dining rooms. Den off of kitchen with door to screened porch overlooking the fenced back yard. Hardwood floors in 3 bedrooms upstairs and master bathhas been newly renovated with a tile shower and vessel sink. Downstairs offers unfinished laundry area, 2 more bedrooms and a bonus/media/office areawith French doors outside. Basement has been waterproofed and offers a lifetime, transferrable warranty from B Dry Waterproofing. Newer roof witharchitectural shingles, New 3 ton heating unit 7/08. Just around the corner from Lake Forest Elementary and close to everything!
